Class WebMessageAdapter

    • androidx.webkit.internal.WebMessageAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.chromium.support_lib_boundary.FeatureFlagHolderBoundaryInterface, org.chromium.support_lib_boundary.WebMessageBoundaryInterface

    public class WebMessageAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.chromium.support_lib_boundary.WebMessageBoundaryInterface
    Adapter between WebMessageCompat and WebMessageBoundaryInterface. This class is used to pass a PostMessage from the app to Chromium.
